snippet.title: Johnny Depp Reveals He Doesn't Regret Marrying Amber Heard

Johnny Depp Reveals He Doesn't Regret Marrying Amber Heard
The relationship between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp has had its ups and downs. When the former couple was involved in a long legal fight, they had only been married for two years. Amber Heard's relationship with Johnny Depp has been tumultuous to say the least. From the classic dog smuggling event to Amber's bombshell divorce filing, the pair had it all throughout their four years together. Since they called it quits, there have been allegations of abuse, several defamation lawsuits, and countless court appearances for the two stars.
